PASSIVE D OR F BackStab -NOTE- this affect only work behind that mean if riki attack from the front once the target lose all stack
increase riki agility, riki attack will do 100% crit damage behind the target and lowering the armor of the target as well
if the target get 8 stack of Stab he will take increase damage

agility bonus 5 7 9 11
damage multiplier behind the target 110% 120% 130% 140%
armor lost per stack 1
damage increase 10% 13% 16% 19%
damage increase duration 2.5 second
armor lost duration 2.5 second
-NOTE- has no cooldown to regive the stack again meaning that with alot of attack speed the increase damage can stay for infinit time

talent level 15 upgrade BackStab
increase damage multiplier by 10%
increase armor lost per stack by 0.5
increase agility bonus by 4

